<doc>
  <member name="D3D12_TEX2DMS_ARRAY_DSV">
    <summary>
      <para>Describes the subresources from an array of multi sampled 2D textures for a depth-stencil view.</para>
    </summary>
    <remarks>
      <para>Use this structure with a <see cref="D3D12_DEPTH_STENCIL_VIEW_DESC" /> structure to view the resource as an array of multi sampled 2D textures.</para>
    </remarks>
    <seealso href="https://docs.microsoft.com//windows/desktop/direct3d12/direct3d-12-structures">Core Structures</seealso>
  </member>
  <member name="D3D12_TEX2DMS_ARRAY_DSV.FirstArraySlice">
    <summary>
      <para>The index of the first texture to use in an array of textures.</para>
    </summary>
  </member>
  <member name="D3D12_TEX2DMS_ARRAY_DSV.ArraySize">
    <summary>
      <para>Number of textures to use.</para>
    </summary>
  </member>
</doc>